data.eml:eml: Two new species of the genus Foenobethylus Kieffer 1913 (Hymenoptera: Bethylidae) from China with a key to the known species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Liu, Jingxian, Chen, Huayan, Xu, Zaifu (2011): Two new species of the genus Foenobethylus Kieffer 1913 (Hymenoptera: Bethylidae) from China with a key to the known species. Zootaxa 2806: 53-59, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.277079
